56:44.458 --> 56:45.708
Please don't look.

56:46.375 --> 56:49.416
[Sofia whimpering]

56:51.291 --> 56:53.333
[Sofia sobbing]

56:54.083 --> 56:55.875
[crying]

56:59.250 --> 57:02.875
[crying intensifies]

57:02.958 --> 57:05.833
-[squelch]
-[Sofia groaning in pain]

57:17.500 --> 57:19.333
[Riccardo groaning in pain]

57:19.416 --> 57:23.166
[Riccardo groaning loudly]

57:25.166 --> 57:27.500
[grunting in pain]

57:29.500 --> 57:32.000
[shouting in pain]

57:32.583 --> 57:35.375
[tearing]

57:40.666 --> 57:42.958
[screaming]

57:43.041 --> 57:45.541
[sobbing]

57:45.625 --> 57:48.083
[chilling music continues]

57:52.750 --> 57:54.625
[music fades]

57:56.500 --> 57:59.833
[ringing]

57:59.916 --> 58:01.916
[ringing intensifies]

58:10.041 --> 58:12.041
[ringing intensifies]

58:24.875 --> 58:28.250
[hopeless music playing]

58:28.333 --> 58:31.083
[ringing and tongue clicking continue]

58:40.833 --> 58:43.666
[Elisa sobbing]

58:48.000 --> 58:49.291
[swords rasp]

58:52.458 --> 58:54.291
[Elisa sobbing]

58:58.250 --> 59:00.416
[Elisa crying]

59:13.416 --> 59:17.291
We didn't even realize.
It doesn't make sense.

59:17.375 --> 59:19.375
Shh.

59:20.791 --> 59:21.833
I'm so sorry.

59:21.916 --> 59:23.875
[Elisa sobbing]

59:29.208 --> 59:30.750
Is it okay if I hug you?

59:37.333 --> 59:38.500
[sobs]

1:00:03.916 --> 1:00:05.708
We didn't wake up the whole time.

1:00:06.375 --> 1:00:07.458
What was it?

1:00:11.250 --> 1:00:12.541
What are you saying?

1:00:12.625 --> 1:00:13.916
You never drank.

1:00:15.708 --> 1:00:17.291
Why didn't you ever drink?

1:00:17.791 --> 1:00:19.041
Are you crazy?

1:00:23.083 --> 1:00:25.458
Please, Elisa, I can't take this.

1:00:26.333 --> 1:00:27.375
[Elisa whimpers]

1:00:27.458 --> 1:00:29.125
[Fabrizio] It's just you and me.

1:00:32.541 --> 1:00:34.250
I'm so scared, Elisa.

1:00:38.500 --> 1:00:40.041
[Fabrizio sobs] I'm so scared.

1:00:41.416 --> 1:00:44.458
[tense, pulsing music playing]

1:00:47.166 --> 1:00:48.416
[Elisa sniffles]

1:00:48.500 --> 1:00:50.291
[shaky breathing]

1:00:50.375 --> 1:00:52.958
[pulsing music grows faster]

1:00:54.916 --> 1:00:56.875
[woman over earpiece]
Fabrizio, can you hear me?

1:01:00.375 --> 1:01:01.958
Take her under the deer.

1:01:03.375 --> 1:01:05.958
[tense music rising]

1:01:06.041 --> 1:01:07.500
[music stops]

1:01:08.875 --> 1:01:10.375
[woman speaks indistinctly]

1:01:12.500 --> 1:01:15.916
[woman] If you can hear us,
take the girl under the deer.

1:01:16.000 --> 1:01:17.791
Who are you? [sobs]

1:01:19.708 --> 1:01:21.125
I'm Fabrizio. It's me.

1:01:21.625 --> 1:01:24.458
[woman speaks indistinctly]

1:01:25.125 --> 1:01:26.541
[sobs] Who's talking?

1:01:26.625 --> 1:01:28.166
-Nobody.
-Stay back!

1:01:28.250 --> 1:01:30.583
-[sobs]
-[woman] I'm not getting anything useful.

1:01:31.208 --> 1:01:33.666
-Hey.
-[woman] Fabrizio, can you hear me?

1:01:33.750 --> 1:01:36.125
-It's me, Fabrizio.
-[woman] Fabrizio.

1:01:36.208 --> 1:01:39.583
The misfit. The loser.
You guys called me names behind my back.

1:01:40.375 --> 1:01:41.916
[Fabrizio] Come on. Give it to me.

1:01:43.291 --> 1:01:45.375
-Give it to me.
-[whimpers]

1:01:47.208 --> 1:01:49.625
I told you to give it back! What the hell?

1:01:50.500 --> 1:01:51.875
-[sobs]
-[woman] Hello?

1:01:57.625 --> 1:01:58.541
No.

1:01:59.708 --> 1:02:00.666
No.

1:02:01.375 --> 1:02:02.208
No!

1:02:04.625 --> 1:02:05.583
No!

1:02:07.291 --> 1:02:08.250
No!

1:02:11.208 --> 1:02:12.208
No!

1:02:13.208 --> 1:02:14.041
No!

1:02:15.083 --> 1:02:16.083
No!

1:02:16.625 --> 1:02:17.583
No!

1:02:18.291 --> 1:02:20.458
No! No!

1:02:20.541 --> 1:02:22.250
No, you fucking whore!

1:02:23.000 --> 1:02:25.458
You're such a fucking slut!
Total fucking slut!

1:02:25.541 --> 1:02:27.666
You hear me? You've ruined it all!

1:02:27.750 --> 1:02:30.833
You completely ruined it all!
You ruined it all!

1:02:30.916 --> 1:02:32.291
Fucking bitch!

1:02:32.375 --> 1:02:35.166
[brooding music playing]

1:02:51.958 --> 1:02:53.125
[exhales]

1:02:57.958 --> 1:02:59.166
Take her.

1:02:59.250 --> 1:03:03.000
-[approaching footsteps]
-[Elisa whimpering]

1:03:03.083 --> 1:03:05.375
[door slams]

1:03:05.958 --> 1:03:09.875
[Elisa screaming hysterically]

1:03:11.333 --> 1:03:15.708
[screaming continues]

1:03:15.791 --> 1:03:18.500
[Elisa] Help! Help me!

1:03:18.583 --> 1:03:22.250
[Elisa screaming]

1:03:22.333 --> 1:03:23.458
[door slams]

1:03:36.666 --> 1:03:41.166
[cheerful accordion music playing]

1:03:44.541 --> 1:03:47.500
[sizzling]

1:03:50.750 --> 1:03:52.750
[cheerful music continues playing]

1:03:57.000 --> 1:03:59.333
[boy in Italian] Dad, tell me something.

1:03:59.416 --> 1:04:02.291
When Grandpa was heartbroken,
he kept saying,

1:04:02.375 --> 1:04:05.333
"There's no respect anymore!"
Dad, what's respect?

1:04:06.458 --> 1:04:07.708
[moans]

1:04:09.416 --> 1:04:12.916
[boy singing in Italian]
♪ My son, respect is the virtue ♪

1:04:13.000 --> 1:04:16.500
♪ That every Calabrian man
Has in his heart ♪

1:04:16.583 --> 1:04:20.041
♪ This feeling doesn't exist anymore ♪

1:04:20.125 --> 1:04:23.666
♪ Respect is over, and so is honor ♪

1:04:23.750 --> 1:04:27.291
♪ When your granddad
Talked about his past ♪

1:04:27.375 --> 1:04:30.875
♪ And his youth to his children ♪

1:04:30.958 --> 1:04:34.583
♪ He ended up with a broken heart ♪

1:04:34.666 --> 1:04:38.375
♪ Remembering everything
That isn't here anymore ♪

1:04:48.250 --> 1:04:49.541
[in English] Help me.

1:04:50.625 --> 1:04:51.708
[sobs] Please.

1:04:56.333 --> 1:04:57.291
[boy in Italian] Dad.

1:04:57.375 --> 1:05:00.791
Who were the three knights
that Grandpa always talked about?

1:05:10.416 --> 1:05:13.916
♪ The three wise knights he mentioned ♪

1:05:14.000 --> 1:05:17.333
♪ Were three saints of the holy circles ♪

1:05:17.416 --> 1:05:20.791
♪ They brought us the honorable laws ♪

1:05:20.875 --> 1:05:25.458
♪ And we are all devoted to them ♪

1:05:26.333 --> 1:05:27.750
[song ends]

1:05:44.541 --> 1:05:46.500
[in English] A drink
to the Three Knights of Honor.

1:05:47.250 --> 1:05:48.458
To the great patron saints.

1:05:48.541 --> 1:05:53.791
Osso, Mastrosso, and Carcagnosso. Cheers.

1:05:59.583 --> 1:06:01.333
And now, enjoy your meal.

1:06:01.416 --> 1:06:03.416
[forks clanking]

1:06:05.541 --> 1:06:07.541
[whimpering]

1:06:10.625 --> 1:06:15.041
[all imitate whimpering]

1:06:15.125 --> 1:06:18.416
[crying]

1:06:21.666 --> 1:06:26.041
[all imitate whimpering]

1:06:30.041 --> 1:06:30.875
Stop it!

1:06:36.583 --> 1:06:38.583
[mayor humming]

1:06:45.041 --> 1:06:47.041
[flies buzzing]

1:06:57.625 --> 1:06:58.500
Do you see?

1:06:59.333 --> 1:07:00.625
They're all content.

1:07:02.916 --> 1:07:04.500
Because I look after them.

1:07:05.375 --> 1:07:07.291
[mayor] I am everybody's mother.

1:07:09.166 --> 1:07:11.291
Is it true I'm everybody's mother?

1:07:13.375 --> 1:07:14.500
[mayor] They're not mean.

1:07:15.250 --> 1:07:16.875
They're mocking you, yeah?

1:07:18.500 --> 1:07:21.375
But they know you're the most precious
out of everyone.

1:07:26.375 --> 1:07:30.000
If you don't die,
how can I take care of everyone here?

1:07:30.833 --> 1:07:31.708
Huh?

1:07:36.458 --> 1:07:38.333
[mayor] You're so beautiful.

1:07:38.416 --> 1:07:40.291
Such a pretty girl.

1:07:41.291 --> 1:07:42.541
I'm sorry.

1:07:45.333 --> 1:07:47.666
But the Mafia
really isn't what it used to be.

1:07:50.291 --> 1:07:52.208
We must all learn to adapt.

1:07:54.416 --> 1:07:55.500
[car horn honks]

1:07:56.333 --> 1:08:02.083
THREE KNIGHTS CAMPING

1:08:02.166 --> 1:08:06.875
[suspenseful music playing]

1:08:11.291 --> 1:08:12.916
[sobbing] Help me.

1:08:15.625 --> 1:08:17.791
Eat, everyone, or your food will be cold.

1:08:18.750 --> 1:08:21.125
[Elisa crying] Help!

1:08:21.208 --> 1:08:23.291
[crying] Help!

1:08:24.500 --> 1:08:27.541
[Elisa crying] Help me!

1:08:30.208 --> 1:08:31.583
[Elisa shouts] Help!

1:08:32.625 --> 1:08:34.291
[Elisa shouts] Help me!

1:08:38.166 --> 1:08:42.375
[Elisa sobbing]

1:08:44.500 --> 1:08:45.833
[sobbing]

1:08:45.916 --> 1:08:48.000
Help me!

1:08:48.083 --> 1:08:49.375
[car retreating]

1:08:55.875 --> 1:08:57.375
[sobbing]

1:09:05.000 --> 1:09:08.500
[tense music playing]

1:09:27.416 --> 1:09:28.416
[thump]

1:09:33.375 --> 1:09:34.541
[moans softly]

1:09:41.291 --> 1:09:43.291
[ethereal music playing]

1:10:13.291 --> 1:10:15.291
[sobs softly]

1:10:30.375 --> 1:10:32.083
Give us a smile, Mama.

1:10:33.791 --> 1:10:36.166
[sobs softly]

1:10:38.375 --> 1:10:40.250
You filmed everything.

1:10:40.333 --> 1:10:41.541
[Fabrizio] There.

1:10:42.125 --> 1:10:45.083
I have to be honest.
Even if you occasionally screw things up,

1:10:45.166 --> 1:10:47.833
the moment you figure it all out is, like…

1:10:47.916 --> 1:10:50.041
Fuck, it's a real turn-on.

1:10:52.625 --> 1:10:53.708
Where is Chiara?

1:10:54.875 --> 1:10:56.625
What did you do to her?

1:10:56.708 --> 1:10:58.500
No. No spoilers.

1:10:59.833 --> 1:11:01.625
[Elisa] Is this what you do?

1:11:03.708 --> 1:11:06.500
Record videos of people
being tortured and killed?

1:11:07.708 --> 1:11:09.166
They're horror movies.

1:11:12.708 --> 1:11:16.458
[laughing]

1:11:18.083 --> 1:11:20.333
[laughing continues]

1:11:20.416 --> 1:11:21.625
What the fuck?

1:11:22.208 --> 1:11:26.750
[laughing hysterically]

1:11:28.083 --> 1:11:31.750
[Elisa sniffles] So I end up dying
in a loser's fake movie.

1:11:32.750 --> 1:11:36.375
And the villains are actually called Osso,

1:11:36.958 --> 1:11:40.000
Mastrosso, and Ca…

1:11:40.875 --> 1:11:42.333
Caranosso!

1:11:42.416 --> 1:11:44.500
[Fabrizio] Carcagnosso.
It's not complicated.

1:11:44.583 --> 1:11:46.583
They are the three
founding fathers of the Mafia,

1:11:46.666 --> 1:11:49.333
and I turned them into the new
Freddy, Jason, and Leatherface

1:11:49.416 --> 1:11:50.916
'cause I'm a genius.

1:11:52.000 --> 1:11:55.250
If we were in the States,
they would already sign me for a sequel.

1:11:56.000 --> 1:11:57.708
Your movie totally sucks.

1:12:00.291 --> 1:12:02.833
It's just a carbon copy of other films.

1:12:05.125 --> 1:12:07.375
People like you always criticize.

1:12:07.875 --> 1:12:11.666
Then in Italy, all you get are crappy
comedies and shitty YouTube videos.

1:12:11.750 --> 1:12:13.375
In Italy, no one wants to be scared.

1:12:13.458 --> 1:12:17.333
You go to the movies and are like,
"Ew, that's so gross! No."

1:12:17.416 --> 1:12:19.916
"Na, na, na, na, naa!"

1:12:20.000 --> 1:12:21.166
[Fabrizio breathes heavily]

1:12:21.250 --> 1:12:24.250
Except, then, you turn on the TV,
and there's nothing but death.

1:12:24.333 --> 1:12:26.416
24/7. Dead people.

1:12:26.500 --> 1:12:28.291
Because you enjoy it.

1:12:28.375 --> 1:12:31.916
The student who massacres her flatmate,
that's… that's what you like.

1:12:32.000 --> 1:12:33.875
The mother who choked her son.

1:12:33.958 --> 1:12:35.583
Wonderful.

1:12:35.666 --> 1:12:39.250
The husband stabbing his wife.
That's… that's worth more than cocaine.

1:12:41.708 --> 1:12:45.375
And so you're asking me,
why, exactly, am I doing all of this?

1:12:47.291 --> 1:12:48.958
It's what you asked for.

1:12:50.208 --> 1:12:53.333
These are the most requested
forms of content.

1:12:54.041 --> 1:12:55.083
It's the future.

1:12:58.250 --> 1:12:59.250
Not mine.

1:13:00.291 --> 1:13:01.666
Okay. We'll see.

1:13:07.791 --> 1:13:08.916
[moans softly]

1:13:11.125 --> 1:13:12.833
[shaky breathing]

1:13:15.500 --> 1:13:17.416
[squelching]

1:13:17.500 --> 1:13:21.000
[haunting music playing]

1:13:30.541 --> 1:13:32.916
[moaning]

1:13:33.000 --> 1:13:35.000
[shaky breathing]

1:13:36.291 --> 1:13:40.833
[sobbing]

1:13:42.000 --> 1:13:44.541
[sobbing intensifies]

1:13:49.541 --> 1:13:50.750
[moaning]

1:13:53.833 --> 1:13:55.541
